Unisys Corp said shipments will beginin July 1987 of its new security software package to preventunauthorized access to its A series mainframe computers used bycommercial customers and for government installations.    The Infoguard software security module extends the securityfacilities already available on A series computers, it said.    Infoguard may be licensed through a five year extended termpurchase or on a monthly license basis.  The five year ETPranges from 8,450 dlrs on an A 2 mainframe to 34,300 dlrs on anA 15 mainframe, it said. Reuter&#3;